snippet.title: BABY VIDEOS that you DON'T WANT TO MISS! - GET READY to DIE FROM LAUGHING!
snippet.description:
Kids are simply the best! They make you smile with their awesome fails, regardless your daily mood :) Being clumsy makes them so cute and funny at the same time. This funny/cute combination will make your day better! So ridiculous, funny and cute! What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
